"       T4a",
"      </td>",
"      <td>",
"       Moderately advanced disease",
"      </td>",
"     </tr>",
"     <tr>",
"      <td>",
"       Tumor involving deep soft tissue, cartilage, bone, or overlying skin",
"      </td>",
"     </tr>",
"     <tr>",
